This package comprises of the Sendy component and the Sendy module.

## Sendy Component

The Sendy component is a Joomla component that handles the backend logic for the registration form.
It captures the data from the form and stores it the local database and then submits it to the Sendy API.

## Sendy Module

The Sendy module is a Joomla module that displays the registration form on the frontend. It then submits the data to the Sendy component.